zilla x Kong: The New Empire","original_language":"en"},{"id":945961,"adult":false,"title":"Alien: Romulus","video":false,"overview":"While scavenging the deep ends of a derelict space station, a group of young space colonizers come face to face with the most terrifying life form in the universe.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.8151,"vote_count":4295,"poster_path":"/2uSWRTtCG336nuBiG8jOTEUKSy8.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-13","vote_average":7.17,"backdrop_path":"/iYqSQaWDttQIQzsxg9xHyg0bttG.jpg","original_title":"Alien: Romulus","original_language":"en"},{"id":552524,"adult":false,"title":"Lilo & Stitch","video":false,"overview":"The wildly funny and touching story of a lonely Hawaiian girl and the fugitive alien who helps to mend her broken family.","genre_ids":[10751,878,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":16.6407,"vote_count":2022,"poster_path":"/ckQzKpQJO4ZQDCN5evdpKcfm7Ys.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-17","vote_average":7.219,"backdrop_path":"/7Zx3wDG5bBtcfk8lcnCWDOLM4Y4.jpg","original_title":"Lilo & Stitch","original_language":"en"},{"id":1084199,"adult":false,"title":"Companion","video":false,"overview":"During a weekend getaway at a secluded lakeside estate, a group of friends finds themselves entangled in a web of secrets, deception, and advanced technology. As tensions rise and loyalties are tested, they uncover unsettling truths about themselves and the world around them.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.2385,"vote_count":2090,"poster_path":"/oCoTgC3UyWGfyQ9thE10ulWR7bn.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-22","vote_average":7.015,"backdrop_path":"/qA6MHDGDY0LyutjLUgFJRbPXLpW.jpg","original_title":"Companion","original_language":"en"},{"id":803796,"adult":false,"title":"KPop Demon Hunters","video":false,"overview":"When K-pop superstars Rumi, Mira and Zoey aren't selling out stadiums, they're using their secret powers to protect their fans from supernatural threats.","genre_ids":[14,10402,35,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":43.7242,"vote_count":2401,"poster_path":"/zT7Lhw3BhJbMkRqm9Zlx2YGMsY0.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-20","vote_average":8.091,"backdrop_path":"/w3Bi0wygeFQctn6AqFTwhGNXRwL.jpg","original_title":"KPop Demon Hunters","original_language":"en"},{"id":1197306,"adult":false,"title":"A Working Man","video":false,"overview":"Levon Cade left behind a decorated military career in the black ops to live a simple life working construction. But when his boss's daughter, who is like family to him, is taken by human traffickers, his search to bring her home uncovers a world of corruption far greater than he ever could have imagined.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":21.7022,"vote_count":1777,"poster_path":"/6FRFIogh3zFnVWn7Z6zcYnIbRcX.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-26","vote_average":6.686,"backdrop_path":"/fTrQsdMS2MUw00RnzH0r3JWHhts.jpg","original_title":"A Working Man","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":651,"adult":false,"title":"M*A*S*H","video":false,"overview":"One of the world's most acclaimed comedies, M*A*S*H focuses on three Korean War Army surgeons brilliantly brought to life by Donald Sutherland, Tom Skerritt and Elliott Gould. Though highly skilled and deeply dedicated, they adopt a hilarious, lunatic lifestyle as an antidote to the tragedies of their Mobile Army Surgical Hospital, and in the process infuriate Army bureaucrats. Robert Duvall, Gary Burghoff and Sally Kellerman co-star as a sanctimonious Major, an other-worldly Corporal, and a self-righteous yet lusty nurse.","genre_ids":[35,18,10752],"popularity":5.8645,"vote_count":1120,"poster_path":"/on8Q9LhtHYNhmITjUMpgOUkIG8o.jpg","release_date":"1970-02-18","vote_average":6.955,"backdrop_path":"/3YWL6rZmvZxCQw2qEwxPGrqhYku.jpg","original_title":"M*A*S*H","original_language":"en"},{"id":982,"adult":false,"title":"The Manchurian Candidate","video":false,"overview":"Near the end of the Korean War, a platoon of U.S. soldiers is captured by communists and brainwashed. Following the war, the platoon is returned home, and Sergeant Raymond Shaw is lauded as a hero by the rest of his platoon. However, the platoon commander, Captain Bennett Marco, finds himself plagued by strange nightmares and soon races to uncover a terrible plot.","genre_ids":[53,18],"popularity":2.2903,"vote_count":786,"poster_path":"/2xQ856kd9hw6bB3OnusGyTvvkwB.jpg","release_date":"1962-10-24","vote_average":7.517,"backdrop_path":"/bbec0wDUaV8nQnQHC6Fb0fSYwNM.jpg","original_title":"The Manchurian Candidate","original_language":"en"},{"id":249573,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo File 212","video":false,"overview":"A Communist spy ring in Japan is hard at work trying to sabotage the American war effort during the Korean War, using kidnapping, murder and a disturbed former kamikaze pilot. A U.S. secret agent, posing as a reporter, is dispatched to Tokyo to put a stop to these nefarious activities.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":0.2362,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/drVgjWGZU0RgEpEOJYUEV3KBO0A.jpg","release_date":"1951-01-26","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/f8RQg7fH7c7BdZoZ48TnXNtT4La.jpg","original_title":"Tokyo File 212","original_language":"en"},{"id":433850,"adult":false,"title":"The Martyrs","video":false,"overview":"Out of fourteen ministers taken away by the communist troop, only two come back alive. The mystery behind their survival is at the issue here. Told through one of the survivor's testimony, depicts images of men troubled between the war and the religion. Although laden with anti-Communist notions from the 60's military regime.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.258,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/kblHj6iaLOHCfJ7AIemZ58iZ9uZ.jpg","release_date":"1965-06-17","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/tJfTLbcznROMr66cMZF5rhrp7t4.jpg","original_title":"순교자","original_language":"ko"},{"id":18415,"adult":false,"title":"Gummo","video":false,"overview":"Teenagers Solomon and Tummler kill time in Xenia, Ohio, a small town that has never recovered from the tornado that ravaged the community in the 1970s.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":1.4904,"vote_count":688,"poster_path":"/tMdoCRx0XIPR5uYBwxbxR7WCNBb.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-17","vote_average":6.637,"backdrop_path":"/k9ckmSgxUT3TJTxRAFAdYXqD9fQ.jpg","original_title":"Gummo","original_language":"en"},{"id":257746,"adult":false,"title":"Battle on Shangganling Mountain","video":false,"overview":"The film follows a group of Chinese People's Volunteer Army soldiers who are holding Triangle Hill for several days against US forces. Short of both food and water, they hold their ground until the relief troops arrive. The movie portray the battle as a Chinese victory over an American invasion, and the People's Volunteer Army soldiers were shown as Chinese war heroes.\"","genre_ids":[10752,18,36],"popularity":0.1803,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/geskV26OwCivlt5evcVHOca1bXI.jpg","release_date":"1956-12-01","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/ohw5Krq7aGXPGPxpzl7cuJ08AZ2.jpg","original_title":"上甘岭","original_language":"zh"},{"id":10476,"adult":false,"title":"Hustle & Flow","video":false,"overview":"With help from his friends, a Memphis pimp in a mid-life crisis attempts to become a successful hip-hop emcee.","genre_ids":[80,18,10402],"popularity":1.7881,"vote_count":426,"poster_path":"/yO5QTMZ2Oex6mwsgJuwRuINGuOQ.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-22","vote_average":7.141,"backdrop_path":"/d4ZrRcwEPmLQvOCyrSdWw5NglGB.jpg","original_title":"Hustle & Flow","original_language":"en"},{"id":599321,"adult":false,"title":"Korea: The Never-Ending War","video":false,"overview":"Shedding new light on a geopolitical hot spot, the film — written and produced by John Maggio and narrated by Korean-American actor John Cho — confronts the myth of the “Forgotten War,” documenting the post-1953 conflict and global consequences.","genre_ids":[99,10752],"popularity":0.3401,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/5abPj8F14cHtINxbWddbK74XWI3.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-29","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/nidbM1Nq2TKICycDcpLnQRof1PU.jpg","original_title":"Korea: The Never-Ending War","original_language":"en"},{"id":9681,"adult":false,"title":"Casanova","video":false,"overview":"With a reputation for seducing members of the opposite sex, regardless of their marital status, a notorious womanizer discovers a beauty who seems impervious to his charms. However, as he continues to pursue the indifferent lady, he finds himself falling in love.","genre_ids":[12,35,18,10749],"popularity":2.6703,"vote_count":925,"poster_path":"/pp237jqOnlLojQfvCgJHv5yZofL.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-25","vote_average":6.446,"backdrop_path":"/1WQGyi1Z7823obW2dFMddriDgMQ.jpg","original_title":"Casanova","original_language":"en"},{"id":9688,"adult":false,"title":"Melinda and Melinda","video":false,"overview":"While dining out with friends, Sy suggests the difficulty of separating comedy from tragedy. To illustrate his point, he tells his guests two parallel stories about Melinda ; both versions have the same basic elements, but one take on her state of affairs leans toward levity, while the other is full of anguish. Each story involves Melinda coping with a recent divorce through substance abuse while beginning a romantic relationship with a close friend's husband.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.7089,"vote_count":488,"poster_path":"/3cLNqq5dpblYG0QkPgwn763DvJB.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-22","vote_average":6.184,"backdrop_path":"/Nez4mwFX2Y0QSpgyrDKzsskpnB.jpg","original_title":"Melinda and Melinda","original_language":"en"},{"id":9740,"adult":false,"title":"Hannibal","video":false,"overview":"After having successfully eluded the authorities for years, Hannibal peacefully lives in Italy in disguise as an art scholar. Trouble strikes again when he's discovered leaving a deserving few dead in the process. He returns to America to make contact with now disgraced Agent Clarice Starling, who is suffering the wrath of a malicious FBI rival as well as the media.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":1.3969,"vote_count":5084,"poster_path":"/v5wAZwRqpGWmyAaaJ8BBHYuNXnj.jpg","release_date":"2001-02-08","vote_average":6.771,"backdrop_path":"/1eMvglbY3wpl4nl09eYLtfstV2I.jpg","original_title":"Hannibal","original_language":"en"},{"id":263381,"adult":false,"title":"Gilsodom","video":false,"overview":"A middle-aged woman in Busan searches for the son she lost in Gilsodom during the Korean War.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5215,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/qfYwaWER9Lckm19aQnp897epdBA.jpg","release_date":"1986-04-05","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/i1soKMk2Arp5lipe8f5TCUfuzR4.jpg","original_title":"길소뜸","original_language":"ko"},{"id":11658,"adult":false,"title":"Tae Guk Gi: The Brotherhood of War","video":false,"overview":"When two brothers are forced to fight in the Korean War, the elder decides to take the riskiest missions if it will help shield the younger from battle.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,36,10752],"popularity":1.7102,"vote_count":753,"poster_path":"/vyG8qpimh3XSlxc6OmPq8LJRJl.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-05","vote_average":7.983,"backdrop_path":"/oqaKsofz49zjNhi48sxQIq8U73X.jpg","original_title":"태극기 휘날리며","original_language":"ko"},{"id":11699,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call - New Orleans","video":false,"overview":"Terrence McDonagh is a New Orleans Police sergeant, who receives a medal and a promotion to lieutenant for heroism during Hurricane Katrina. Due to his heroic act, McDonagh injures his back and becomes addicted to prescription pain medication. He then finds himself involved with a drug dealer who is suspected of murdering a family of African immigrants.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":2.1224,"vote_count":1232,"poster_path":"/73jnKMm8bCcV1w2ltkaeJfLZJzX.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-11","vote_average":6.183,"backdrop_path":"/abF5X1C7KMJEJnbB7KidfHOIszj.jpg","original_title":"Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call - New Orleans","original_language":"en"},{"id":259946,"adult":false,"title":"Flight Nurse","video":false,"o